52
00:03:13,090 --> 00:03:15,360
OK.

53
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:20,930
Now let's go on to part B. So
now A and B are 3 by 3 similar

54
00:03:20,930 --> 00:03:24,160
matrices with the same
