66
00:04:12,420 --> 00:04:13,310
Good.

67
00:04:13,310 --> 00:04:16,040
Now I'll let you--

68
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:20,560
so before we check it, let's
just say the point.

69
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:23,440
The point is if two matrices
are similar to the same

70
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:26,950
matrix, then they're similar
to each other.

71
00:04:26,950 --> 00:04:30,100
Similarity is a transitive
relation.

72
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:40,140
And I'll just let you check that
you can take TS inverse A

73
00:04:40,140 --> 00:04:48,970
